resources.string: I am an Android developer who has been learning and honing my skills for the past year. I am grateful to the team behind AndroidIDE for providing the opportunity to create apps on mobile devices, even for those who may not have access to a computer. My first major project, PCSO Hub, took me two months to develop and I am proud of the end result. However, due to financial difficulties, I am currently unable to make it available on the Google Play Store. If you have enjoyed using PCSO Hub, I would greatly appreciate your support in the form of a donation to help me publish it on the Play Store. With your help, we can make this app widely available and accessible to even more users.

PCSO Hub is an application that provides lotto results drawn by the Philippine Charity Sweepstakes Office (PCSO) for informational purposes only.
We make every effort to ensure that the information on our site is up-to-date and accurate, but we cannot guarantee its reliability, completeness, or accuracy. Any decisions made based on the information provided on our application are at your own risk, and we will not be held liable for any losses or damages that may result.
Please take a moment to read our Privacy Policy to understand the data we collect and why we collect it. When accessing other websites, it is important to be aware that their privacy policies and terms of use may differ from PCSO Hub\'s and may not be under our control.
We do our best to maintain the website, but PCSO Hub cannot be held responsible for any temporary technical difficulties that may cause the site to be unavailable.
It is important to note that we do not claim ownership of any lotto results, logos, or other information displayed on our application. PCSO Hub is not affiliated with PCSO. Our goal is to provide informative content and share it with our audience.
For official confirmation and any other questions, we suggest visiting the PCSO\'s official website
